properties.areaDesc: Sand Island to Bayfield WI; Port Wing to Sand Island WI
properties.headline: Gale Watch issued January 4 at 3:49AM CST until January 6 at 12:00AM CST by NWS Duluth MN
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 20 to 25 knots with gusts up to 40 knots and
waves 5 to 9 feet possible.

* WHERE...Port Wing to Sand Island WI and Sand Island to
Bayfield WI.

* WHEN...From Sunday afternoon through Sunday evening.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds can cause hazardous waves which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should consider altering plans to avoid possible
hazardous conditions.  Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter
course, and/or secure the vessel for severe wind and waves.

NWSheadline: GALE WATCH IN EFFECT FROM SUNDAY AFTERNOON THROUGH SUNDAY EVENING
